<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Of course you can! You may be confused about the characters appearances to some extent. However all you have to do to fix that problem, is look up a q<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Of course you can! You may be confused about the characters appearances to some extent. However all you have to do to fix that problem, is look up a quick description online. Christie does an excellent job of allowing to book to be picked up and read by a person who has no experience of the series. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
