        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3024869786" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16742678161246998081">A clever mystery, as you would expect from Agatha Christie. For some reason, I didn&apos;t love it as much as the others I&apos;ve read though. I had very little interest in the characters themselves, and I found the resolution to be a little strange. But still an interesting and engaging read!</span>
  <span id="freeText16742678161246998081" style="display:none">A clever mystery, as you would expect from Agatha Christie. For some reason, I didn't love it as much as the others I've read though. I had very little interest in the characters themselves, and I found the resolution to be a little strange. But still an interesting and engaging read!</span>
